definitions.definition: A cultivated plant, belonging to the genus Delphinium , with tall blue-colored spikes containing flowers; a larkspur .
A shade of blue , named for the flowers.

main_definition: ( countable ) A cultivated plant, belonging to the genus Delphinium , with tall blue-colored spikes containing flowers; a larkspur .
secondary_definitions: ( countable and uncountable ) A shade of blue , named for the flowers.
